# IWXXM TBox — supplementary domain axioms for the lakehouse reasoner
#
# Pairs with: iwxxm-ruleset-domain_range.rules (so rules 1, 7, 8 fire).
# Base URI:   matches what iwxxm-engine emits (IwxxmConstants.BASE_URI).
#
# Note on namespaces: IwxxmRdfWriter unifies the iwxxm: and aixm: tags it
# encounters in a message under the single IWXXM base URI, so AIXM features
# embedded in METAR / TAF / SIGMET messages (e.g. the aerodrome the report
# refers to) appear as iwxxm:AirportHeliport, iwxxm:Airspace, etc. The TBox
# below declares those embedded-AIXM classes under the IWXXM namespace.
#
# Out of scope on purpose: data cardinality, datatype constraints, WMO Codes
# Registry codelists (those are SKOS, not OWL-RL), and anything else the
# OWL 2 RL fragment does not handle.

@prefix rdf:   <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix owl:   <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix iwxxm: <http://example.org/bigkgolap/atm/iwxxm#> .

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Embedded-AIXM feature classes  (exercises Rule 1: subClassOf)
#
# Declaring these gives the reasoner a target for the rdfs:range axioms
# below; without the declaration, range-derived types would still be
# produced but downstream queries would have no class to roll up to.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------

iwxxm:AirportHeliport a rdfs:Class .
iwxxm:Airspace        a rdfs:Class .

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Property typings  (exercises Rules 7 & 8: domain / range)
#
# Property names match what IwxxmRdfWriter emits (the local part of
# iwxxm:* / aixm:* tags, stripped of the namespace prefix).
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------

iwxxm:aerodrome
    a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:range iwxxm:AirportHeliport .

iwxxm:affectedFIR
    a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:domain iwxxm:SIGMET ;
    rdfs:range  iwxxm:Airspace .

iwxxm:issuingAirTrafficServicesRegion
    a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:range iwxxm:Airspace .
